Text: hey honeyyou Well im really glad I decided to give you a call tonight It was really nice to talk to you I do miss you and I am glad you didnt end up getting married Im really sorry I was such a spaz back then I guess I was just scarred I can honestly say Im over that I really like talking to you I only wish you lived closer Maybe someday right Well sweetie Im gonna try to get to bed now I wish you could see the smile on my face Well ill send you a picture of me in flight attendant training just incase you forgot what i looked like However my hair is longer now but you get the idea talk to you soon smooches trina

hi sweetiebaby Thanks for the message on my cell today I was at the gym when I got it and it instantly put a smile on my face So how was your day Mine was ok kinda hectic though I felt like I was rushing all over town all day By the way my hair looks awsome too bad you cant see it Well I kinda missed hearing from you today I mean atleast getting an email from you Im sure you were busy working so its ok I mean atleast someone was working today So are we really going to the Kentucky Derby in May I really think itll be fun Plus it would be like old times seeing you again Hopefully well get together much sooner than that Oh im really sorry but I havent remembered the name of that movie yet Wont you tell me it so you can put me out of my misery Pretty Please Anyways I do remember other things though Like meeting you for lunch at the Black Tulip and how cute you always looked in you suits Plus there is always the first time we met at the new years eve party You know when you put your class ring on my finger and asked me to have your kids I bet you didnt remember that one now did you Well honey I guess im gonna get off here and go to bed Im really not looking forward to tomorrow but just maybe some secret admirer will send me flowers or something Well im not counting on it but you never know Have a great day tomorrow and ill talk to you soon smooches trina ps miss you
